api_list.description:
For IG login, you need to use your own proxies, as our proxies are used on millions of requests and can often be blocked from IG login!
IG is also attentive to the IP addresses from which you enter, so use the same proxies so that IG does not block your accounts.
Our proxies change all the time and are poorly suited for Instagram authorization.

optional_parameters.name: proxy
optional_parameters.description: We recommend that you specify your proxies so that Instagram does not block your account! In the following format: `http://username:password@host:port`

optional_parameters.name: verification_code
optional_parameters.description: From your TOTP application, such as Google Authenticator
